{
  "skill": "sk-doc",
  "version": "2.0.0.0",
  "description": "Declarative packet registry for the sk-doc parent hub: workflowMode + packetKind + backendKind + toolSurface + advisorRouting for each documentation-authoring workflow packet. The advisor routes the single sk-doc identity; the hub selects the workflow packet. Workflow-only hub (no surface axis), zero named extensions. SCAFFOLD STATE: registry authored; packet bodies + shared/ populated in later phases; hub SKILL.md/graph-metadata/description swap deferred to cutover.",
